#

Sweet Nutella and Banana Crepes

30 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairyEggsNuts (from Nutella)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

French

Course:

Dessert

Tags:

DessertBreakfastEasyQuick

Description

Deliciously thin crepes filled with rich Nutella and sweet bananas, perfect for breakfast or dessert!

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • milk: 1 cup
  • eggs: 2
  • butter (melted): 2 tablespoons
  • bananas: 2 (sliced)
  • nutella: 1/2 cup
  • powdered sugar (optional): for dusting
